<a href="http://allafrica.com/stories/201305311613.html " target="_self">http://allafrica.com/stories/201305311613.html</a></p><p><i>East African Business Week</i>, ‘Milk exports fetch US$11.5 million’, 3 April 2013</p><p>
<a href="http://allafrica.com/stories/201304090368.html " target="_self">http://allafrica.com/stories/201304090368.html</a></p><p><i>New Vision</i> (Kampala), ‘Keep off unprocessed milk, minister warns’, 20 March 2013</p><p>
